HEADWORD: Pomiferous
<hw>Po*mif"er*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>pomifer</ets>; <ets>pomum</ets> fruit + <ets>ferre</ets> to bear:
cf. F. <ets>pomif⟦egrave⟧re</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd>
<def>Bearing pomes, or applelike fruits.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>Bearing
fruits, or excrescences, more or less resembling an apple.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

